headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid ADI and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Analog Devices trades at $204.41 per share and has moved almost in lockstep with the market over the last six months. The stock has lost 7.3% while the S&P 500 is down 5.8%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
